Changed Connect in Apex Input Classes

ConnectApi.CartInput: added customFields property
  - Array of sObjects and custom fields for the sObjects.
ConnectApi.CartItemInput: added customFields property
  - Array of sObjects and custom fields for the sObjects.
Salesforce CMS:
  - ConnectApi.ManagedContentDocumentInput: added apiName property
    - API name of the managed content.
  - ConnectApi.ManagedContentPublishInput: added contextContentSpaceId property
    - ID of the context workspace.
  - ConnectApi.ManagedContentUnpublishInput: added contextContentSpaceId property
    - ID of the context workspace.
title: Salesforce Summer '24 Release Notes: ConnectApi Cart and Managed Content Changes
